request.description: Registers a new user with the provided information and returns a success response upon successful registration.
Authenticates a user by validating their email and password and provides an access token upon success.

request.description: Creates an organization invitation with a generated token and sends an email invitation to the specified email address.

variable.description: The ID of the organization to update.

request.description: Updates an organization's information if the authenticated user is an admin.
Retrieves a list of organizations that are not marked as deleted.

item.name: Search for users by name or email.

variable.description: The name or email to search for.

request.description: Searches for users based on the provided name or email and returns a list of matching users.
Retrieves a list of users with their basic information.
